<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/creator> "John Frederic Brüne"@en .
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description> "Draft schema (TBox only) for comparing national IP laws against WIPO treaty minimum standards. Built following Palmirani's MeLOn methodology, reusing FRBR (frbr:) for the document layer and LegalRuleML's metamodel (lrmlmm:) for the statement layer. Covers CQ1-CQ9 (national side); the treaty side (CQ10) is in the separate treaty_draft.ttl, marked as discussion material. Worked examples (Ireland, India, Kenya) that validate this schema against real statute text live in examples.ttl, kept separate on purpose: this file stays a stable, roughly constant-size schema no matter how many jurisdictions the pipeline eventually covers (up to ~200), while worked examples grow one file per batch of countries. Split 2026-07-23."@en .
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title> "WIPO IP Ontology (draft)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "WIPO IP Ontology (draft)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "draft, 2026-07-23" .
