<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#ExceptionOrLimitation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "a country-specific carve-out from Copyright, e.g. Ireland's fair dealing for research; classified by one or more ExceptionKind." .
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#ExceptionOrLimitation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Exception or Limitation" .
