<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#ProtectionTerm> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "how long a Copyright lasts: a value, a unit, and the event it is counted from." .
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#ProtectionTerm> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Protection Term" .
