# 
# https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#RightKind
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#RightKind> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#RightKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "matches the Economic Rights hierarchy in Garcia & Gil's Copyright Ontology (JURIX 2008): Reproduction, Distribution, Communication (with Broadcasting and Making Available as subtypes), Transformation (with Adaptation and Translation as subtypes), Fixation. That hierarchy refines the four top-level ExploitationRight classes (Reproduction, Communication, Distribution, Transformation) in Delgado et al.'s earlier IPROnto (JURIX 2003). All eight individuals below have a direct counterpart in the 2008 version." .
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#RightKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Right Kind" .
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#RightKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://jurix.nl/pdf/j03-12.pdf> .
<https://w3id.org/wipo-ip#RightKind> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://rhizomik.net/html/~roberto/papers/rg-losw08.pdf> .
